Package: xed-tui
Version: 1.022
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.11)
Maintainer: XED-dev <hello@xed.dev>
Description: Terminal browser and session manager for Claude Code
 XED /TUI is a zero-dependency curses-based TUI for browsing, searching,
 and managing Claude Code sessions stored as JSONL files in
 ~/.claude/projects/. Inspired by mutt (email) and ranger (file browser).
 .
 Features: 4-panel layout, Markdown rendering, full-text search, tags,
 notes with smart sync, session resume, multi-language help overlay.
Homepage: https://tui.xed.dev
